* text=auto eol=lf
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.webp binary
uv.lock linguist-generated=true
package-lock.json linguist-generated=true

# Built frontend bundle — committed (not gitignored) so git clone / a touch-manager
# git update carries the real served artifact, and force-shipped to the Comfy
# Registry via [tool.comfy] includes in pyproject.toml. Treat as generated:
# collapse/exclude in GitHub diffs+stats, suppress the noisy minified textual diff,
# and keep current-branch copy on merge (the bundle is regenerated, never hand-merged).
web/dist/** linguist-generated=true -diff -merge
